OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779825947
OL,3,CSeveral people reportedly killed after
OL,4,Cschool bus hit by train in Belgium
OL,6,FMultiple people have reportedly been
OL,7,Fkilled after a school bus was hit by a
OL,8,Ftrain at a level crossing in Belgium.
OL,10,FThe vehicle was hit in Buggenhout,
OL,11,FEast Flanders, around 8am local time
OL,12,Fon Tuesday, according to railway
OL,13,Fnetwork operator Infrabel.
OL,15,FFlemish broadcaster VRT News reported
OL,16,Fthat several people had been killed in
OL,17,Fthe incident, but no police statement
OL,18,Fhas been issued.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/6
