OL,3,CSeveral people reportedly killed after
OL,4,Cschool bus hit by train in Belgium
OL,6,FThe broadcaster said the bus contained
OL,7,Fseven secondary school children, one
OL,8,Fchaperone and the driver.
OL,10,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,11,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,12,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,13,Finbox every Friday morning.
OL,15,FPolice at the scene said family
OL,16,Fmembers were being informed of the
OL,17,Fincident.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/6
