OL,3,CSeveral people reportedly killed after
OL,4,Cschool bus hit by train in Belgium
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Buggenhout
OL,7,FMunicipality told ITV News the heads
OL,8,Fof multiple emergency services were in
OL,9,Fdiscussion and there would be a press
OL,10,Fbriefing later on Tuesday.
OL,12,F"With great dismay, I learned of the
OL,13,Ftragic accident in Buggenhout, where a
OL,14,Fschool bus was struck by a train,"
OL,15,FBelgium's Interior Minister Bernard
OL,16,FQuintin wrote on X on Tuesday.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,309,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30804
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779825947
OL,3,CSeveral people reportedly killed after
OL,4,Cschool bus hit by train in Belgium
OL,6,F"My thoughts go out to the victims and
OL,7,Ftheir loved ones. I wish the injured
OL,8,Fmuch strength. Thank our emergency
OL,9,Fservices for their swift response on
OL,10,Fsite."
OL,12,FJustice Minister Annelies Verlinden
OL,13,Fwrote online that "words fail" at the
OL,14,Fincident, which she described as a
OL,15,F"tragedy".
OL,17,F"Thank you to the emergency services
OL,18,Fand the police for their swift
OL,19,Fintervention and their sustained
OL,20,Fefforts on site," Verlinden said.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/6
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
