PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F308A1779825947
OL,3,CSeveral people reportedly killed after
OL,4,Cschool bus hit by train in Belgium
OL,6,F"The prosecutor's office is, of
OL,7,Fcourse, also continuing to follow up
OL,8,Fon this accident."
OL,10,FA large police presence remains at the
OL,11,Fscene, and train services between
OL,12,FDendermonde and Londerzeel have been
OL,13,Fcancelled, VRT News reported.
OL,15,FThis is a breaking news story, more to
OL,16,Ffollow soon...
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/6
